¶In memory of Marcelle Hanson, beloved mother, grandmother
and aunt, who died aged 96 on 13 January, 2016.
She adored nature and spent many happy hours in this park."¨
©John K.J.' Sommerfeld - engineer and renowned inventor of portable runway track for aircraft.
Lilian Sommerfeld - beloved matriarch, centenarian, and company secretary."ģ
